F-35 comes in two versions, infernal robotics vtol and stock standard flight only, instructions for operation are included in the plane description of the vtol model. Both can be downloaded [here](https://www.dropbox.com/sh/eu4koba2kqfwg90/AACoP7oMHCKa8opz3vgsLduea?dl=0)

Dig it. Hard trying to fit the turbojet into the fuselage though. And the basic engine is crazy underpowered. I haven't figured it out yet.
